\id GAL - Nchane
\h Galɛshiaŋ
\toc1 Ŋwa wù Bol gɛ̀ saŋ fɛ kintaashɛ ki Galɛshiaŋ le
\toc2 Galɛshiaŋ
\toc3 Gal
\mt2 Ŋwa wù Bol gɛ̀ saŋ fɛ kintaashɛ ki
\mt1 Galɛshiaŋ le
\imt1 Fiɛɛ fì le a Ŋwa wu Galɛshiaŋ wunɛ le
\ip Gɛ̀ bee sege bo gɛ̀ kɛ ki bo fêeji saaka wù joŋe kune Jiso, bamii ba le gɛ Bajuu gɛ fii wa saaka wuyu wunɛ, bamii bamu ja bo kɛ bo too bɛ n'yɛyɛ wù le lɛ bo kɛ̂me ki bo gɛ̂ɛde banchi ba Musɛ bachii, fede munchii ki bo chvûse bamii ba le gɛ Bajuu gɛ yeh fɛ bo tu bo nyûme bamii ba Kletu ba nchiɛɛŋ nchiɛɛŋ.
\ip Ŋwa wunɛ wù Bol gɛ̀ saŋ fɛ bamii ba Galɛshiaŋ le gɛ̀ bee ki wu tɛ̂ɛŋ bvufee bvuboo bvu kâasɛ bvu tû yi fiɛɛ fì kooji le. No wu le mwa wu ntuŋ wu Jiso noo, wu mo wu saaŋe wu gɛɛne fwe wu duunyi chuule lɛ Nyo jode muh lɛ wu le jialɛ sɛŋ a wu jii nyû nje fitele fì wu leese yi Kletu le.
\iot Bikwɛɛ bi mwɛɛ mù le a Ŋwa wunɛ le
\io1 1:1-10 Fɛŋkɛɛ
\io1 1:11–2:21 Bvuŋga bvu Bol njɛ mwa ntuŋ wu Jiso Kletu
\io1 3:1–4:31 Bol jɛmɛ kune saaka wù joŋe mo banchi
\io1 5:1–6:10 Bamii ba le ba Kletu le bo bu wa yi bvunfa le bo yuge wa nyu Kiyo ki Yuude le
\io1 6:11-18 Kimɛsɛ
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Ŋwa wunɛ saŋ mɛ wù Bol, mwa ntuŋ wu Jiso Kletu. Gɛ mɛ nyu mwa ntuŋ wù tuŋ muh wu wuŋ gɛ kɛnɛ nya muh bvuŋga mɛne gɛ. Gɛ̀ tuŋ Jiso Kletu bɛ Nyo wù Chiji wù gɛ̀ bvusɛ wu yi kwe le.
\v 2 Mɛ bɛ booŋ ba bwee wene ba mbɛmɛ bachii ba le fɛnɛ besa bo yɛɛse bɛŋ bintaashɛ bi bamii ba mbɛmɛ bi woŋ wù Galɛshiaŋ le.
\v 3 Nyo wù Chiji wese besabɛŋ bɛ Tada Jiso Kletu dûnyɛ fitele fì joŋe fɛ bɛŋ le, bo ka bo nyâ bɛŋ bɛ muntele mù nyiɛgee.
\v 4 Jiso Kletu le wu wù gɛ̀ nya kikwɛɛ ke nje bimbefɛ biɛsa wu lɛ wu bvûsɛ besabɛŋ chiaaŋ yi woŋ wu kimbefɛ kì mɛɛse kinɛ le. Finɛ le no Nyo wù le Nyo mo Chiji wese besabɛŋ gɛ̀ seesɛ.
\v 5 Bvukugɛ bvuchii le kɛme wu segechii bvù kage gɛ. Fi nyûme noo.
\s1 Saaka wù joŋe kune Jiso Kletu mɛ gɛh wu mumwaa
\p 
\v 6 Jwe yune lo mɛ lɛ gɛh mɛɛse mɛɛse nɛ bɛŋ ja wa bɛŋ baa jiŋ Nyo wù gɛ̀ tɛŋe bɛŋ nje fitele fì joŋe fì Kletu kɛme fɛ bɛŋ le, bɛŋ tu bɛŋ bii nyu saaka wù joŋe wumu le yeye.
\v 7 Gɛ nyu lɛ saaka wù joŋe wumu le yu yeye gɛ. Fi le gɛh lo lɛ bamii bamu goone ki bo fîise bvufee bwena, bo chɛ̂ŋe bɛ saaka wù joŋe kune Kletu.
\v 8 Mɛ mo njɛme lɛ kɛnɛ nyu nchɛndaa wu Nyo wumu wù fɛwe wù feeji saaka wumu yeye bɛŋ le njɛ le wɛɛ wù bee gɛ̀ feeji bɛŋ le sɛŋ, mwɛdɛ tûu loŋ!
\v 9 No bee gɛ̀ jɛmɛ wa ŋka tuu fo ki njɛ̂me lɛ, nɛ muh jâ wu feeji saaka wumu wù yeye njɛ le wɛɛ wù bɛŋ gɛ̀ fi sɛŋ, mwɛdɛ tûu lɛ loŋ!
\p 
\v 10 Bɛŋ kwaji lɛ ŋgoone lɛ bɛ̂ɛŋse bamii mɛ noo, lɛ bɛ̂ɛŋse Nyo lɛ? Noo, lɛ bɛŋ kwaji lɛ ŋgoone ki ŋgêe lɛ bamii yûge njoŋ le? Nɛ bee lɛ ŋgoone ki ŋgêe lɛ bamii yûge nyu njoŋ, ŋgɛ nyû muh wu lɛme wu Kletu gɛ.
\s1 Saaka wù joŋe wu Bol gɛ̀ feeji gɛ̀ dunyi Kletu wu le
\p 
\v 11 Booŋ ba bwɛɛŋ, ŋgoone lɛ bɛŋ kɛ̂ɛ lɛ saaka wù joŋe wu Nyo wù ŋgɛ̀ feeji bɛŋ le gɛ̀ bee fiɛɛ fi gɛ bu a muh wu wuŋ le gɛ.
\v 12 Gɛ ŋgɛ̀ n'yu jwe wu muh le gɛ, gɛ nyu muh wù gɛ̀ yɛyɛ mɛ yu gɛ. Gɛ̀ dunyi Jiso Kletu mɛne.
\v 13 Njɛme nɛ nje bɛŋ gɛ̀ bee bɛŋ yu wa no kinche kaŋ gɛ̀ shee ki nyume sege ŋgɛ̀ mbaaŋ mbii mbɛmɛ wese wu Bajuu le. Ŋgɛ̀ shee mboonɛ bikaa a je yì befe le a bintaashɛ bi bamii ba mbɛmɛ ba Nyo jiŋ ŋgoone ki nchîijɛ lo bi.
\v 14 Ŋgɛ̀ ŋgɛɛne fwe yi mbɛmɛ wese wu Bajuu le nfede lo kighaŋ kaŋ antɛnɛɛ a bamii besa, nfiee lo wesee yi kinche ki woŋ ki bachiji besa le.
\v 15 Geenɛ Nyo gɛ̀ baa wa mɛ wu gɛɛ mbaaŋ a bwɛɛŋ shɛŋ. Fitele fie fì joŋe fì wu gɛ̀ dunyɛ mɛne ge wu tɛɛŋ mɛ.
\v 16 Wu gɛ̀ dunyɛ Mwa ye mɛne no wu gɛ̀ goone, wu lɛ njîɛnyi nfêeji kune wu bamii ba le gɛ Bajuu le gɛ. No wu gɛ̀ dunyɛ noo, ŋgɛ ŋka mbiide fiɛɛ muh wu wuŋ le gɛ.
\v 17 Ŋgɛ̀ mbaaŋ bɛɛŋ gɛ tɛ Yɛlusalɛm ki n'yɛ̂ŋ bamii ba gɛ̀ bee wa booŋ ba ntuŋ ba Jiso a mɛ fwe le gɛ. Ŋgɛ̀ nja ŋgɛɛŋ fiaŋ nyu Alɛbia, nja yo ŋkaasɛ ntu jiŋ Damasku.
\p 
\v 18 Lɛ to nyu ajiŋ a biluŋ bitɛde mbɛɛŋ Yɛlusalɛm lɛ besa Bita kɛ̂ɛ ye yese. No ŋgɛ̀ mbɛnɛ, besa wu che aju yuufe ncho atɛŋ.
\v 19 Ŋgɛ̀ mbaaŋ ŋka yɛŋ gɛ muh mu ŋgoo yi booŋ ba ntuŋ ba Jiso le fede Jɛm wù mwa bwee Tada wese besabɛŋ wù Jiso le gɛ.
\v 20 Fiɛɛ fì nsaŋe finɛ le nchiɛɛŋ, Nyo kee lɛ gɛ mbiane lo gɛ.
\v 21 Gɛ̀ bee kife kimu le, nja ŋgɛɛŋ bimbe bì Silia bɛ bì Silisia le.
\v 22 Segekɛɛ gɛ̀ bee bintaashɛ bi bamii ba Kletu bi kimbe kì Judia le gɛ kee wa mɛ ajii gɛ.
\v 23 Bo gɛ̀ yuge gɛh lo bamii jɛme lɛ, “Muh wɛɛ wù chi boone bikaa a besabɛŋ jiŋ jiɛnyi wa mɛɛse wu feeji lɛ bamii lêese muntele yi Kletu le, nyu fiɛɛ fì wu chi shee wu goone lɛ wu chîijɛ lo.”
\v 24 Lɛ bo yu noo bo tu bo tume maŋkuŋ ma Nyo yi fiɛɛ fì wu ge fɛ mɛne.
\c 2
\s1 Booŋ ba ntuŋ ba Jiso tooŋ saaka wu Nyo wù Bol gɛ̀ feeji
\p 
\v 1 Gɛ̀ bee ajiŋ a biluŋ yuufe ncho binɛh, ŋka mbɛɛŋ Yɛlusalɛm besa Banaba. Sege ŋgɛ̀ mbɛɛne, njo Taytu.
\v 2 Ŋgɛ̀ mbɛɛne kife kinɛ le, dunyi Nyo lɛ mbɛ̂ɛŋ. No ŋgɛ̀ mbɛnɛ, n'yɛŋ bamii ba bo gɛ̀ kee bo lɛ le bikwɛɛ, besa bo kɛŋsɛ yo, ŋgiisɛ saaka wù joŋe wu Nyo wù ŋgɛ̀ feeji bamii ba le gɛ Bajuu le gɛ a bo jii. Ŋgɛ̀ gee noo wu lɛ keefɛ lɛme chì ŋgɛ̀ lɛŋ wa bɛ chì mbaaŋ nlɛne lɛ̂sɛ achiji gɛ.
\v 3 Lɛ bo yu noo, bo gɛ ka bo lɛ̂me lɛ ba chvuu Taytu yeh wù besa wu gɛ̀ bee mo no wu gɛ̀ bee muh wu Baglek gɛ.
\v 4 Gɛ̀ baaŋ nyu gɛ nje bamii bamu ba gɛ̀ mbiane lɛ bo le bamii ba mbɛmɛ gɛ, ba gɛ̀ wɛnɛ bo lee fɛ bee gɛ̀ bee fo, tu bo gɛ̀ baaŋ gɛ bɛ njɛme ki bo lee fifiɛɛ le gɛ. Bamii bamu banɛ gɛ̀ to njɛ bantuŋkee ki bo keeyɛ no bee gee wa mwɛɛ yase yase nje bee le be taashɛ besa ba Kletu Jiso. Bo mo bo goone ki bo kâasɛ bo chvûu bee bvunfa le.
\v 5 Bee faŋ ki bee bɛ̂ɛŋ lo mo fiɛɛ fì bo gɛ̀ too bɛ fi le, mo shige. Bee gɛ̀ gee noo wu lɛ bee goone ki be gɛ̂ɛ kinchiɛɛŋ kì le ki saaka wù joŋe wu Nyo wunɛ fɛ bɛŋ le.
\v 6 Bamii baa ba bo gɛ̀ kee lɛ le bikwɛɛ, bo gɛ̀ baaŋ taa gɛ fiɛɛ yi fiɛɛ fì ŋgɛ̀ feeji le gɛ. (Kɛnɛ bo gɛ̀ bee la, kɛnɛ la, tu gɛ fifiɛɛ kɛme fiɛɛ fɛ mɛne gɛ, nje gɛ Nyo duunyi yeye yeye gɛ.)
\v 7 Geenɛ, bo tu bo yɛŋ lɛ bo le bo nya saaka wù joŋe wu Nyo chiaaŋ yaŋ le, lɛ nfêeji bamii ba le gɛ Bajuu le gɛ, yɛɛŋyɛɛŋ no bo le bo nya Bita le, lɛ wu fêeji Bajuu le.
\v 8 Fi le lɛ Nyo wù gɛ̀ nya bvuŋga Bita le lɛ wu lɛ̂ne lɛme chinɛ njɛ mwa wu ntuŋ fɛ Bajuu le, le gɛh wu wù gɛ̀ nya mɛne lɛ nlɛ̂ne njɛ mwa wu ntuŋ fɛ bamii ba le gɛ Bajuu le gɛ.
\v 9 Lɛ bo doo bo yɛŋ je yì Nyo le wu baa mɛ yu, Jɛm bɛ Bita mo Joŋ ba bo gɛ̀ kee lɛ le chikfu chi bamii ba mbɛmɛ, bo mo bo nya kibo besa Banaba le ki bo dûnyɛ lɛ besa bo lɛne yi fiɛɛ le fimimia. Besa bo mo bee bɛɛŋ lɛ bee gɛ̂ɛŋ bee lɛ̂ne fɛ bamii ba le gɛ Bajuu le gɛ, bo lɛ̂ne fɛ Bajuu le.
\v 10 Fiɛɛ fì ba gɛ̀ jɛmɛ gɛ̀ bee gɛh lɛ bee tâne Bajuu ba kifufe. Finɛ nyu fiɛɛ fì ŋgɛ̀ ŋkoŋe baaŋ ki ŋgêe.
\s1 Bol sa Bita Antiok
\p 
\v 11 Gɛ̀ bee kife kimi le, Bita ja wu to Antiok, nsa wu a wu jii nje wu gɛ̀ ge jialɛ baaŋ.
\v 12 Fi le lɛ wu gɛ̀ ya wu to wu jii mwɛɛ bɛ bamii ba le gɛ Bajuu gɛ, wu nyiɛŋse gɛ. Bamii bamu ba Jɛm gɛ̀ tuŋ doo bo to, wu mo wu kɛ wu chiide ye jiŋ, wu ja wu ga, wu gɛ ka wu jii mwɛɛ bɛ bo gɛ. Wu gɛ̀ gasɛ noo nje wu gɛ̀ faane ŋgoo yì gɛ̀ lɛme gɛh lɛ ba kɛme ki ba chvûse muh wù le gɛ muh wu Bajuu gɛ yeh fɛ mwɛdɛ nyû muh wu Kletu.
\v 13 No wu ge noo bamii ba mbɛmɛ bamu ba gɛ̀ bee Bajuu mo bo bege bɛ gee che chiyu chì wu jɛme yeye wu gee yeye. Mo Banaba kibɛɛ mo wu jiiŋ wu bi tɛ gee chiboo chiyu le.
\v 14 Ndoo yɛŋ lɛ gɛ gee chiboo bii nchiɛɛŋ nchiɛɛŋ no saaka wù joŋe wù kune Kletu duunyi gɛ, mɛ mo njɛmɛ Bita le a bo bachii jii lɛ, “Wo le muh wu Bajuu, wo chee wa njɛ muh wù le gɛ muh wu Bajuu gɛ, wo goone ki wo kâane bamii ba le gɛ Bajuu gɛ ki bo chêe njɛ Bajuu, nɛɛ?”
\p 
\v 15 Ŋgɛ̀ njɛme Bita le noo nyu nchiɛɛŋ lɛ besa bo le booŋ ba woŋ wu Bajuu. Gɛ bee nyume bamii ba le gɛ Bajuu gɛ ba bo yɛne lɛ le bamii ba befe gɛ.
\v 16 Geenɛ bee kee gɛh lɛ gɛ Nyo jode muh lɛ wu le jialɛ sɛŋ nje wu gɛɛde banchi gɛ. Wu jode nje wu le wu leesɛ fitele yi Jiso Kletu le. Mo bee Bajuu kibɛɛ le be leesɛ tɛ fitele yi Kletu Jiso le wu lɛ bee nyûme jialɛ sɛŋ a Nyo jii nyume gɛ nje bee gɛɛde banchi gɛ. Fi le lɛ gɛ muh wù gɛɛde banchi, Nyo nyume wu yû wu jô wu lɛ wu le jialɛ sɛŋ gɛ.
\p 
\v 17 Nɛ bee mone ki be nyû jialɛ sɛŋ a Nyo jii nje bee le bamii ba Kletu, bamii ka tu yɛne gɛh lɛ bee le bamii ba befe nje gɛ bee gɛɛde banchi ba Bajuu gɛ, tu fi le lɛ Kletu toone kimbefɛ? Gɛ fi nyu noo gɛ mbɛŋ.
\v 18 Nɛ nja ŋka ŋkɛ njoone je yi banchi nyu fiɛɛ fì ŋgɛ̀ nsaayɛ wa, tu fifiɛɛ duunyi lɛ nle muh wù ŋgode lo nchi.
\v 19 Fiɛɛ fì le, le lɛ a kimbe ki banchi le, nle wa ŋkfusa, nyu banchi ba yuuyi mɛ, ŋkwe, wu lɛ nchêe wa no Nyo goone.
\v 20 Taŋlo ndu lɛ ba le ba ta wa mɛ yi kintaaŋ le, ŋkwe besa Kletu. Gɛ kinche kì ŋkɛme mɛɛse ka nyume kaŋ gɛ. Chee wa Kletu yi ye yaŋ le. Kinche kì ŋkɛme mɛɛse yi ye yaŋ le, le nje fitele fì nleese yi Mwa Nyo le. Wu gɛ̀ dunyɛ kiŋkoŋɛ fɛ mɛne wu nya kikwɛɛ ke ki wu kwê nje mɛ.
\v 21 Gɛ taŋlo nfaŋ fitele fì joŋe fi Nyo ki wu bvûsɛ bamii gɛ. Nɛ le lɛ taŋlo muh nyû jialɛ sɛŋ a Nyo jii nje wu gɛɛde banchi, tu kwe yi Kletu gɛ̀ bee achiji.
\c 3
\s1 Kune banchi bɛ no ba lêesɛ fitele yi Kletu le
\p 
\v 1 O ooo bamii ba Galɛshiaŋ, bɛŋ le la biyuŋ nɛ? Muh le wu noŋ loŋ bɛŋ le? Le gɛh bɛŋ ba ba le ba najɛ wa waaŋ no ba gɛ̀ ta Jiso Kletu yi kintaaŋ le bɛŋ yɛŋ fi chuunyi andaŋandaŋ?
\v 2 Ŋgoone ki mbîih fiɛɛ fimimia bɛŋ le. Kiyo ki Nyo gɛ̀ to yi ye yene le nje bɛŋ gɛ̀ gee no banchi duu noo nje bɛŋ gɛ̀ bɛɛŋ fiɛɛ fì bɛŋ gɛ̀ yu wa le la?
\v 3 Bɛŋ le la biyuŋ nɛ? Bɛŋ kɛ fiɛɛ bɛ Kiyo ki Nyo, bɛŋ tu nyu wa mɛɛse lɛ bɛŋ lé bɛŋ mɛ̂sɛ nyu bɛ bvuŋga bwena?
\v 4 Bɛŋ le bɛŋ yɛŋ baŋgɛ baaŋ achiji? Gɛ n'yɛne lɛ le achiji gɛ.
\v 5 Nyo nyaa Kiyo ke bɛŋ le wu ka gee biŋgha bi mwɛɛ a bɛŋ ntɛnɛɛ nje la? Wu gee noo nje bɛŋ gɛɛde banchi kɛnɛ lɛ le nje bɛŋ le bɛŋ yu wa saaka wù kune Kletu bɛŋ bɛɛŋ wu le?
\p 
\v 6 Le no ba saŋ kune Ablaham a Ŋwa wu Nyo le lɛ,
\q1 “Wu gɛ̀ bɛɛŋ Nyo le,
\q1 Nyo mo wu jo wu lɛ wu le muh wù chaaŋ.”
\p 
\v 7 Bɛŋ yɛŋ la lɛ le bamii ba leesɛ fitele yi Nyo le, le bo ba le kfuu chi Ablaham kibɛɛ.
\v 8 Ŋwa wu Nyo gɛ̀ yu wa wu dunyɛ baaŋ lo lɛ Nyo lé wu gê wu jô bamii ba le gɛ Bajuu gɛ bo nyûme jialɛ sɛŋ a wu jii nje fitele fì bo le bo leesɛ yi ye ye le. Ŋwa wu Nyo mo wu fejɛ saaka wù joŋe wunɛ Ablaham le baaŋ lo wu duu lɛ,
\q1 “Nyo lé wu gê wu nôŋ kimbonɛ yi bituŋ le bichii bi yi kikwɛɛ ki nshɛŋ le nje wo.”
\p 
\v 9 Noo, fi mo fi nyu lɛ bamii ba leesɛ fitele yi Nyo le, Nyo lé wu nôŋ kimbonɛ yi bo le no wu gɛ̀ noŋ tɛ kimbonɛ yi Ablaham wù gɛ̀ leesɛ fitele yi ye ye le.
\p 
\v 10 Bamii bachii ba yɛde lɛ taŋlo bo nyû jialɛ sɛŋ a Nyo jii nje bo gɛɛde banchi, bo tuude nyu loŋ yi bikwɛɛ biboo le, nje ba le ba saŋ lɛ,
\q1 “Muh wuchii wù chee gɛ no ba saŋ a Ŋwa wu banchi le gɛ,
\q2 wu gee gɛ no banchi bachii goone gɛ,
\q1 tu wu tuude loŋ yi kikwɛɛ ke le.”
\m 
\v 11 Fi mo fi duunyi waaŋ lɛ gɛ taŋlo Nyo jô muh lɛ wu le jialɛ sɛŋ nje mwɛdɛ gɛɛde banchi gɛ. Le fiɛɛ fì ba le ba saŋ lɛ,
\q1 “Le gɛh muh wù Nyo le wu jo lɛ wu le jialɛ sɛŋ nje fitele fì wu lese yi ye ye le,
\q1 le wu wù lé wu kɛ̂mɛ kinche.”
\p 
\v 12 Gɛ banchi kɛme fiɛɛ fì bo gê bɛ nleesɛ fitele yi Nyo le gɛ. Fi tu nyu lɛ, “Muh wù gɛɛde banchi lé wu chêe wu bîi gɛh nyu bo le.”
\v 13 Kletu gɛ̀ be wu suuŋ besabɛŋ chiaaŋ yi loŋ wù banchi gɛ̀ to bɛ wu le. Wu gɛ̀ tuu baloŋ besa yi kikwɛɛ ke le, nyu no ba saŋ lɛ,
\q1 “Loŋ le yi muh wù ba le ba shɛŋshɛ yi kite le.”
\p 
\v 14 Wu gɛ̀ ge noo, wu lɛ kimbonɛ kì Nyo gɛ̀ nya wa Ablaham le ki tô tɛ fɛ bamii ba le gɛ Bajuu le gɛ nje Kletu Jiso, wu lɛ besabɛŋ ba leesɛ fitele yi ye ye le kɛ̂mɛ tɛ Kiyo ki Nyo kì wu gɛ̀ ka wa.
\s1 Gɛ banchi taŋlo bo kûsɛ ŋka wu Nyo gɛ
\p 
\v 15 Booŋ ba bwɛɛŋ, besabɛŋ jô mbejɛ yi mwɛɛ mù bamii to bo gee aju achii. Nɛ bamii le bo seesɛ wa fiɛɛ bo ji leh, tu gɛ taŋlo muh kâ wu kûsɛ kɛnɛ wu tâa fiɛɛ fo gɛ.
\v 16 Kune baŋka ba Nyo ba wu gɛ̀ ka fɛ Ablaham bɛ mwa wù lé wu gê wu bû a kfuu che le. Ba baaŋ saŋ gɛ lɛ, “Ba le fɛ booŋ bò lé bo gê bo bû a kfuu che le gɛ.” Fifiɛɛ duunyi lɛ gɛ nyû fɛ bamii le wesee gɛ. Fi duunyi lɛ fi jɛme kune mwa wu mumwaa, mwa wunɛ le Kletu.
\v 17 Fiɛɛ fì ŋgoone ki ndû le lɛ, Nyo gɛ̀ bee wu ge ŋka wunɛ, biluŋ gɛ̀ fe gii yinɛh bɛ kicho mbaanshɛ (430) fɛ wu nyâ banchi. No fi le noo, gɛ taŋlo banchi ba gɛ̀ to ajiŋ ka bo kûsɛ maŋkaŋ mà Nyo gɛ̀ gwo fweele, wu lɛ fiɛɛ fì wù gɛ̀ ka wa lɛsɛ achiji gɛ.
\v 18 Nɛ fi fɛnɛ le lɛ muh taŋlo wu kɛ̂mɛ kimbonɛ kinɛ nyu gɛh sege wu gɛ̂ɛde banchi, tu gɛ ka baaŋ lɛ Nyo gɛ̀ ka lo bamii yu gɛ. Geenɛ, Nyo gɛ̀ nya Ablaham le wu bii no wu gɛ̀ ka wu yu.
\p 
\v 19 Fishaŋ fi banchi le la? Ba gɛ̀ taade banchi ki ba duunyi mwɛɛ mù bamii jiaade kɛge noo gɛɛne bude sege mwa wunɛ wù Nyo gɛ̀ ge ŋka wunɛ kune wu, lé wu gê wu tô. Nyo mo wu nya banchi banɛ banchɛndaa be le, bo mo bo nya chiaaŋ yi muh mu le lɛ wu fêesɛ bamii le.
\v 20 Bɛŋ kee lɛ nɛ bamii ja bo seesɛ fiɛɛ muh mu nyu a bo ntɛnɛɛ, tu wu le fɛ bo le bachii. Geenɛ, Nyo le gɛh wu maa\f + \fr 3:20 \ft Fɛnɛ fi le a je a je lɛ Nyo le wu mumwaa.\f*.
\p 
\v 21 No fi le noo, tu taŋlo nchi ka wu tɛ̂ɛnyi fiɛɛ fì Nyo gɛ̀ ka wa? Gɛ nyu no fi le noo gɛ! Nɛ nchi wumu gɛ̀ bee yu wu taŋlo wu nyâ kinche, tu taŋlo muh nyûme chaaŋ a Nyo jii nje wu gɛɛde banchi nchiɛɛŋ nchiɛɛŋ.
\v 22 Geenɛ, Ŋwa wu Nyo duu lɛ muh wuchii le nfwa a bimbefɛ kuu. Fi mo fi nyu lɛ ŋka wù Nyo gɛ̀ ka fɛ muh wù le wu leesɛ fitele yi Jiso Kletu le, le gɛh wuwɛɛ muh wù leesɛ fitele yi ye ye le wu le wu kɛme.
\s1 Banchi gɛ̀ bee njɛ ndɛ mwa
\p 
\v 23 Gɛ̀ bee fweele Jiso baaŋ a to gɛ wu lɛ bamii lêese fitele yi ye ye le gɛ, bamii nyu a banchi kuu bo kaaŋ bo njɛ bamii ba ncha, bo chiɛɛne gɛɛŋ bu sege Nyo lé wu gê wu dûnyɛ Jiso bo le, bo lêesɛ fitele yi ye ye le.
\v 24 Banchi gɛ̀ bee njɛ ndɛ mwa wù gɛ̀ shee bɛ bamii wu naji gɛɛŋ bu sege Kletu gɛ̀ to, wu lɛ bamii lêesɛ fitele yi ye ye le, fɛ Nyo jô bo lɛ bo le jialɛ sɛŋ a wu jii.
\v 25 No Kletu le wu to wa bamii leesɛ fitele yi ye ye le, tu gɛ besabɛŋ baaŋ chiaaŋ yi ndɛ mwa wunɛ le gɛ.
\v 26 Bɛŋ ba le bɛŋ taashɛ bena ba Kletu Jiso, le wa booŋ ba Nyo bachii nje fitele fì bɛŋ leese yi Kletu le.
\v 27 Bɛŋ kêe lɛ muh wuchii wù ba le ba leesɛ wa a joo, ba taashɛ bɛ Kletu, le wu tu wa bɛ Kletu yi fiɛɛ le fimimia.
\v 28 Gɛ muh mu ka nyume yeye lɛ wu le muh wu Bajuu kɛnɛ muh wù nyume gɛ muh Bajuu gɛ. Gɛ muh mu ka nyume yeye lɛ wu le nfwa kɛnɛ mwa yeh gɛ, gɛ muh mu ka nyume yeye lɛ wu le jwɛŋsɛ kɛnɛ kwɛse gɛ. Bɛŋ bachii le wa yi fiɛɛ le fimimia yi Kletu Jiso le.
\v 29 No bɛŋ le wa bamii ba Kletu noo, tu bɛŋ le wa booŋ ba Ablaham, bɛŋ lé bɛŋ gê bɛŋ kɛ̂mɛ mwɛɛ mù Nyo gɛ̀ ka Ablaham yu.
\c 4
\p 
\v 1 Fiɛɛ fì nduu le lɛ, muh nɛ le ki wu jî bvushɛ bvu chiji, geenɛ wu baaŋ mwa wù shige, tu gɛ yeye nyu yu bɛ nfwa wu chiji gɛ, mo nyu wu wù kɛme bvushɛ bvuyu bvuchii.
\v 2 Wu lé wu ya wu nyûme bamii bamu jîiŋe fɛ wu le, bvushɛ bvuyu nyu chiaaŋ yi bamii bamu le bo jiiŋe fo, gɛ̂ɛŋ bû kife kì chiji seese le.
\v 3 Le gɛh no fi le fɛ besabɛŋ le. Gɛ̀ bee sege besabɛŋ gɛ̀ bee njɛ booŋ ba shige, bee nyu nfa yi mwɛɛ mù sage yi woŋ kfunɛ le.\f + \fr 4:3 \ft Mwɛɛ mù sage yi woŋ kfunɛ le taŋlo nyu banchi mo biyo.\f*
\v 4 Sege kife kì chuule gɛ̀ to ki kojɛ, Nyo tuŋ Mwa ye wu to, kwɛse boo wu, wu tu wu nyu tɛ a banchi kuu.
\v 5 Wu gɛ̀ to wu lɛ wu sûuŋ bamii ba le a banchi kuu, Nyo mo wu jô besabɛŋ njɛ booŋ be.
\v 6 No Nyo jo wa besabɛŋ njɛ booŋ be noo, wu mo wu chiiŋsɛ Kiyo ki Mwa ye lɛ ki tô a muntele mwesa besabɛŋ le. Le ki kì tɛŋe wu lɛ, “Aba,\f + \fr 4:6 \ft Aba le a jɛ́ yi Alamaik le lɛ Chii.\f* Chii.”
\v 7 Fi le lɛ Nyo le wu ge wa lɛ bɛŋ baaŋ gɛ nfa gɛ. Bɛŋ le wa booŋ ba yeh. No bɛŋ le wa booŋ, tu fi le lɛ bɛŋ lé bɛŋ kɛ̂mɛ mwɛɛ mù wu gɛle fɛ booŋ be le.
\s1 Bol faane lɛ bamii ba Galɛshiaŋ le bo jiaa wa je
\p 
\v 8 Gɛ̀ bee fweele sege bɛŋ gɛ̀ baaŋ a kɛɛ gɛ Nyo gɛ, bɛŋ lɛne bvunfa chiaaŋ yi mwɛɛ mù bɛŋ gɛ̀ jode lɛ le banyo nyume gɛ banyo gɛ.
\v 9 Geenɛ, mɛɛse no bɛŋ le bɛŋ kɛɛ wa Nyo, kɛnɛ lɛ mɛɛse no Nyo le wu kɛɛ wa bɛŋ no mbee ki njɛ̂mɛ, bɛŋ jiɛnyi nɛɛ fɛ bɛŋ gôone ki bɛŋ tûu jiŋ fɛ banyo ba achiji banɛ le, ba le njɛ bo kɛme bvuŋga sɛŋ. Bɛŋ goone ki bɛŋ ka bɛŋ tûu nfa yi banyo bayu banɛ le, nje la?
\v 10 Bɛŋ gɛɛde yuuŋ aju a mu le, a mu nyume a baaŋ baaŋ, bɛŋ banɛ kii yimi, bɛŋ banɛ bife bimi yi kiluŋ le, bɛŋ banɛ biluŋ nje la?
\v 11 Bɛŋ gee nɛ nfaane baaŋ lɛ lɛme chì nlɛŋ a bɛŋ ntɛnɛɛ le chi lɛ̂sɛ achiji.
\p 
\v 12 Booŋ ba bwɛɛŋ, ŋkude lo chiaaŋ bɛŋ le lɛ bɛŋ kûsɛ bɛŋ nyû njɛ mɛ, gɛh no ŋgɛ̀ ŋkusɛ mɛ nyume njɛ bɛŋ, sege bɛŋ gɛ̀ baaŋ a kɛmɛ gɛ banchi gɛ. Bɛŋ gɛ̀ baaŋ ge gɛ fiɛɛ fì befe fɛ mɛne gɛ.
\v 13 Bɛŋ kee lɛ fweele sege ŋgɛ̀ nfeeji saaka wù joŋe wu Nyo bɛŋ le gɛ̀ bee nje ŋgɛ̀ nchɛne lo.
\v 14 Mo no ŋgɛ̀ bee yi kinchɛŋ le nɛ, ki gɛ̀ bee njɛ mmoŋ wu gɛ̀ to fɛ bɛŋ le, bɛŋ gɛ̀ baaŋ legɛ gɛ, kɛnɛ bɛŋ nyiɛŋsɛ mɛ gɛ. Bɛŋ ka jode lo mɛ ye yene le njɛ nchɛndaa wu Nyo wumu kɛnɛ njɛ Kletu Jiso kibɛɛ.
\v 15 Bɛŋ gɛ̀ yuge njoŋ bɛ mɛ sege kɛɛ, kooshi la mɛɛse? Taŋlo njɛ̂mɛ lɛ nɛ je gɛ̀ bee yu ki bɛŋ bâayɛ ajii a wene bɛŋ nyâ mɛne, tu bɛŋ gɛ̀ baayɛ gɛh lo.
\v 16 Nle ntu wa muh wu kimbanɛ fɛ bɛŋ le no nsɛŋe nchiɛɛŋ bɛŋ le?
\v 17 Bamii baa goone ki bo dûunyi lɛ bo kɛme kiŋkoŋɛ fɛ bɛŋ le baaŋ, geenɛ bo goone bɛŋ yi fiɛɛ le nyû gɛ fì joŋe gɛ. Bo koŋe lɛ besabɛŋ gâsɛ lɛ bɛŋ kɛ̂me kiŋkoŋɛ nyu fɛ bo le.
\v 18 Fi joŋe lɛ muh kɛ̂me kiŋkoŋɛ fɛ muh le yi fiɛɛ fì joŋe le. Finɛ le chuule segechii, nyu gɛ lɛ sege nle besabɛŋ maa gɛ.
\v 19 Booŋ baŋ ba le shɛ́ŋ yaŋ, nle gɛh njɛ mbaaŋ ŋka ŋkɛ lo lume chena, n'yɛŋ ŋgɛ ŋgɛ̂ɛŋ mbû no kinche ki Kletu le ki nyû ye yene le!
\v 20 Muh jô lɛ mbe mbee besabɛŋ mɛɛse, wu lɛ ŋkûsɛ je yì njɛme yu bɛŋ le. Fiɛɛ fì bɛŋ ge finɛ le bvufee lɛsɛ lo mɛ.
\s1 Yeye yeye wu booŋ ba Ablaham
\p 
\v 21 Bɛŋ ba goone ki bɛŋ nyû a banchi kuu, bɛŋ sɛ̂ɛŋ la mɛ, bɛŋ yuge gɛh fiɛɛ fì banchi jɛme?
\v 22 Ba le ba saŋ lɛ Ablaham gɛ̀ kɛme booŋ ba bilɛŋsɛ bafɛɛ, wu gɛ̀ boo wumu bɛ kwɛse wù le nfwa, wu boo wumu bɛ kwɛse wù le gɛ nfwa gɛ.
\v 23 Nfwa wunɛ gɛ̀ boo mwa gɛh no ba to ba boyi booŋ bachii. Geenɛ kwɛse wù le gɛ nfwa gɛ wɛɛ gɛ̀ boo we mwa wu bii ŋka wù Nyo gɛ̀ fɛ le.
\v 24 Taŋlo besabɛŋ jo fiɛɛ finɛ njɛ mbejɛ wu fiɛɛ. Bikɛse ba bafɛɛ banɛ duunyi maŋkaŋ mà manfɛɛ. Aga wù gɛ̀ bee nfwa jode kijusɛ ki maŋkaŋ mà Nyo gɛ̀ gwo bɛ bamii ba Ishwala yi Mbegɛ wu Sina le. Bamii bachii ba le akuu a maŋkaŋ mayu le nfa.
\v 25 No Aga jode kijusɛ ki maŋkaŋ ma yi Mbegɛ wu Sina wù le woŋ wù Alɛbia le, wu ka wu jode tɛ kijusɛ ki kilaantɛŋ kì Yɛlusalɛm wù mɛɛse le, nje bamii ba a kilaantɛŋ kiyu le bachii le nfa a banchi kuu.
\v 26 Geenɛ bamii ba Yɛlusalɛm wù fɛwe le gɛ nyu nfa gɛ. Wuwɛɛ Yɛlusalɛm le bwee wese besabɛŋ.
\v 27 Le fiɛɛ fì ba gɛ̀ saŋ lɛ,
\q1 “Wo wù kwɛse wù le kaa wu boyi gɛ, wo lâŋeye.
\q1 Wo wù gɛ̀ baaŋ a luŋ gɛ wa mwa gɛ, wo kwâase chike.
\q1 Wo kêe lɛ booŋ ba kwɛse wù ba le ba baa jiŋ wu le,
\q1 bo lé bo dûude bo fêde ba kwɛse wù le bɛ jwɛŋsɛ.”
\p 
\v 28 Noo, booŋ ba bwɛɛŋ, bɛŋ le booŋ ba Nyo bii no Nyo gɛ̀ ka yɛɛŋyɛɛŋ no Ablaham gɛ̀ boyɛ Asik bii no Nyo gɛ̀ ka.
\v 29 Gɛ̀ bee kife kiyu le, mwa wù ba gɛ̀ boyɛ no ba boyi booŋ bachii, tu wu boone bikaa ajiŋ a mwa wù gɛ̀ nya Kiyo ki Nyo bvuŋga fɛ ba boo wu. Le gɛh tɛ yɛɛŋyɛɛŋ bɛ fiɛɛ fì kooshi mɛɛse.
\v 30 Ba le ba saŋ a Ŋwa wu Nyo le kune fiɛɛ finɛ lɛ la? Ba le ba saŋ lɛ,
\q1 “Kûŋɛ bɛ kwɛse wù le nfwa bɛ mwa ye bachii,
\q1 nje gɛ mwa nfwa taŋlo wu gâ bvushɛ bɛ mwa kwɛse wù le gɛ nfwa gɛ.”
\p 
\v 31 No fi le noo booŋ ba bwɛɛŋ, fiɛɛ fì njɛme fichii duunyi lɛ gɛ besabɛŋ nyu booŋ ba kwɛse wù le nfwa gɛ. Besabɛŋ le nyu booŋ ba kwɛse wù le gɛ nfwa gɛ.
\c 5
\s1 Kletu le wu bvusɛ wa besabɛŋ yi bvunfa le
\p 
\v 1 Kletu gɛ̀ bvusɛ wa besabɛŋ yi bvunfa le. Wu gɛ̀ bvuse nɛ, wu lɛ keefɛ besabɛŋ ka be nyûme a bvunfa bvu banchi kuu gɛ. Noo, bɛŋ mo bɛŋ lɛ̂me bɛŋ tɛɛme. Keefɛ bɛŋ ka bɛŋ lêe akuu a kimbuŋ ki bvunfa le gɛ.
\v 2 Bɛŋ yêgɛ bɛŋ yû fiɛɛ fì mɛ wù Bol nlé njɛ̂mɛ. Nɛ bɛŋ bɛme lo lɛ ba chvûu bɛŋ yeh fɛ bɛŋ nyû chaaŋ a Nyo jii, tu fiɛɛ fì Kletu gɛ̀ ge fɛ bɛŋ le le achiji.
\v 3 Ŋka njɛme nchiise lɛ muh wuchii wù le wu bɛɛŋ lɛ ba chvûu wu yeh wu kêe lɛ wu kɛ̂me ki wu gɛ̂ɛde banchi ba Bajuu bachii no bo le.
\v 4 Bɛŋ bachii ba goone ki bɛŋ nyû jialɛ sɛŋ a Nyo jii le nje bɛŋ gɛɛde banchi, bɛŋ kêe lɛ bɛŋ le bɛŋ ŋga wa bikwɛɛ biɛna bɛ Kletu. Bɛŋ le bɛŋ bvusɛ wa ye yene yi mbalɛ wù Nyo bale bɛŋ yu le.
\v 5 Fɛ besabɛŋ le, fiɛɛ fì besabɛŋ jiiŋe fwe yi fi le, le lɛ Nyo lé wu gê wu jô besabɛŋ njɛ bamii ba le chaaŋ a wu jii. Finɛ le fiɛɛ fì Kiyo ki Nyo kì lɛne yi ye yese besabɛŋ le fede yi fitele fì besabɛŋ leese yi Kletu le fi ge wa lɛ besabɛŋ chîɛɛne.
\v 6 Bɛŋ kêe lɛ nɛ muh le wu taashɛ wa bɛ Kletu Jiso, wu nyume ba chvuu wu yeh kɛnɛ ba baaŋ chvuu gɛ wu yeh gɛ, tu gɛh fifiɛɛ kɛme fiɛɛ ki fi gê gɛ. Fiɛɛ fì le fishaŋ le fitele fì wu lesɛ yi Kletu le, wu duunyi yi kiŋkoŋɛ le.
\p 
\v 7 Bɛŋ chi shee bɛŋ gee chuule, ge yɛɛŋ lɛ bɛŋ lû ki bɛŋ bîi nchiɛɛŋ le?
\v 8 Gɛ nyu Nyo wù gɛ̀ tɛŋɛ bɛŋ wu tefɛ bɛŋ a yinɛ je le gɛ.
\v 9 Gɛ bɛŋ kwaji ŋgaŋ wù ba to ba ma lɛ, “Kikuu kimimia chɛŋe bɛ nchwa gɛ?”
\v 10 Ŋgɛɛde bvufee yi ye yene le nje Tada lɛ gɛ bɛŋ bii fiɛɛ fì bamii bamu jɛme le fuge fì jɛme mɛ gɛ. Lɛ muh wɛɛ wù chɛŋe bɛ bvufee bwena, kɛnɛ le yɛɛŋ, le Nyo wù lé wu nôŋ ŋgɛ yi ye ye le.
\v 11 Booŋ ba bwɛɛŋ, nɛ fi bee lɛ mbaaŋ nfeeji lɛ ba chvûse bamii yeh fɛ bo nyûme chaaŋ a Nyo jii, bamii ka bo boone bikaa a mɛ jiŋ nje la? Nɛ fi bee noo tu fiɛɛ fì nfeeji lɛ Kletu gɛ̀ kwe yi kintaaŋ le, bamii yuge bo ka baŋse lo yu, fi gɛ ka fi nyu yu gɛ.
\v 12 Fɛ bamii baa ba njiŋse bɛ bvufee bwena, ŋgoone lɛ ba gɛ̂ɛŋ fwe ba mɛ̂sɛ ba bvûushɛ lo ye yiboo.
\p 
\v 13 Booŋ ba bwɛɛŋ, Nyo gɛ̀ tɛɛŋ wa bɛŋ wu lɛ keefɛ bɛŋ ka bɛŋ nyû nfa yi fiɛɛ fimi le gɛ. Geenɛ, no bɛŋ baaŋ gɛ yi bvunfa le gɛ, keefɛ bɛŋ mo bɛŋ jôde lɛ taŋlo bɛŋ gêe mwɛɛ mù mbefe no nyaŋ yi ye yene goone gɛ. Bɛŋ lɛ̂ne lo lɛme fɛ booŋ ba bwe bena le bɛ kiŋkoŋɛ.
\v 14 Bɛŋ gêe noo nje banchi bachii le bo taashɛ yi wunɛ le wu mumwaa lɛ,
\q1 “Wo kôŋe muh wù le mbebe yo le gɛh no wo koŋe kikwɛɛ kuŋ.”
\m 
\v 15 Geenɛ, bɛŋ nɛ ja bɛŋ tu bɛŋ ŋase lɛbɛŋlɛbɛŋ njɛ bvú, muh goone ki wu lûŋ wu jî lo mwa bwee, bɛŋ yɛ̂ne lɛ keefɛ bɛŋ gê bɛŋ jâ bɛŋ chɛ̂ŋɛ bɛ bikwɛɛ biɛna gɛ.
\s1 Gɛ muh wù chee no Kiyo ki Nyo duunyi // to wu ka wu gee no nyaŋ yi ye goone gɛ
\p 
\v 16 Fiɛɛ fì njɛme le lɛ, bɛŋ chêe bɛŋ bii gɛh no Kiyo ki Nyo duunyi bɛŋ le, noo bɛŋ gɛ ka bɛŋ gêe no nyaŋ yi ye yene goone lɛ bɛŋ gêe gɛ.
\v 17 Njɛme nɛ nje gɛ fiɛɛ fì nyaŋ yi ye goone to fi chɛŋsɛ a fi Kiyo ki Nyo goone le gɛ. Gɛ fì Kiyo ki Nyo goone tɛ fi chɛŋsɛ a fì nyaŋ yi ye goone le gɛ. Gɛ mwɛɛ mù munfɛɛ munɛ taŋlo mu nyûme yì fiɛɛ le fimimia gɛ. Nɛ fiɛɛ fì gɛ taŋlo bɛŋ gêe fiɛɛ fì bɛŋ goone gɛ.
\v 18 Nɛ bɛŋ chee bɛŋ bii nyu no Kiyo ki Nyo duunyi bɛŋ le, bɛŋ gɛ ka bɛŋ nyû a banchi ba Musɛ kuu gɛ.
\v 19 Mwɛɛ mù mbefe mù nyaŋ yi ye to yi goone gɛh bamii maa mu gɛ. Le ki ba jâŋe kinjaŋ bɛ ki ba kwâji mwɛɛ kune kinjaŋ mo ki ba chêe kinche ki nyiɛŋ yi kinjaŋ.
\v 20 Ka nyume ki ba bûune banyo ba achiji bɛ ki ba lâde kɛnɛ ba fîɛŋe jiaaŋ. Ka nyume ki bâne kimbanɛ, ki ba ŋâse kiŋase, ki ba ghɛ̂ge kiŋghɛ, ki ba kɛ̂me shɛ́ŋ yì toonyi bɛ fɛ muh kwâji gɛh nyu kikwɛɛ ke. Ka nyume ki ba gâse bamii mo fɛ muh gâ bamii wu kɛme ke kinchvu.
\v 21 Le tɛ ki ba bɛ̂ɛne kindoŋ, ki ba mûu mbvuuŋ ma kôode bɛ ki bo mûu bo yôde, mo ki bo gêe mumu mwɛɛ njɛ munɛ. Njɛme nchiise no ŋgɛ̀ njɛmɛ wa bɛŋ le fweele, lɛ bamii ba gee munɛ mwɛɛ gɛ bo nyu bo kɛ̂me kijusɛ antɛnɛɛ a bvunfoŋ bvu Nyo gɛ.
\p 
\v 22 Geenɛ, mwɛɛ mù jade fɛ Kiyo ki Nyo le, le munɛ, kiŋkoŋɛ, kilaŋye, nyiɛgee, ŋkanɛ shɛ́ŋ, kiŋge kì joŋe, bvujoŋɛ, ki muh lɛme yi nchiɛɛŋ le,
\v 23 kiŋge kì bonɛ, mo ki muh jiji ye ye le. Gɛ nchi wumu nyume yu wù banɛ mwɛɛ munɛ gɛ.
\v 24 Bamii ba le ba Kletu Jiso le ba ta wa nyaŋ yi ye yiboo bɛ mwɛɛ mù mbefe mù nyaŋ yi ye goone yi kintaaŋ ki Jiso le.
\p 
\v 25 No besabɛŋ chee mɛɛse yi bvuŋga bvu Kiyo ki Nyo le, besabɛŋ mo be gêe mwɛɛ bee bîi gɛh no Kiyo kiyu duunyi.
\v 26 Keefɛ besabɛŋ chîaase ye gɛ. Keefɛ besabɛŋ gêe muntele befe bamii bamu gɛ. Keefɛ besabɛŋ bɛ̂ɛne kindoŋ bɛ bamii bamu gɛ.
\c 6
\s1 Bamii ba Nyo fîih bamii bachii
\p 
\v 1 Booŋ ba bwɛɛŋ, nɛ bɛŋ ja bɛŋ yɛŋ muh mu a bɛŋ ntɛnɛɛ wu gwe yi kimbefɛ le, bɛŋ ba chee kinche no Kiyo ki Nyo duunyi, bɛŋ môŋ ki bɛŋ têfɛ wu wu bû a kimbefɛ kiyu ntɛŋ. Geenɛ, muh doo wu teefe wu teefe wɛɛ wu yɛ̂ne lɛ keefɛ wu tɛ lêe mmoŋ le wu gwê gɛ.
\v 2 Bɛŋ fîih booŋ ba bwe wene bɛ baŋgɛ baboo. Nɛ bɛŋ gee noo tu bɛŋ gɛɛde nchi wu Kletu.
\v 3 Nɛ muh jode kikwɛɛ ke lɛ wu le fiɛɛ, njɛ wu le fiɛɛ sɛŋ, tu wu lɛɛde gɛh nyu bɛ kikwɛɛ ke.
\v 4 Muh wuchii tâa gee che, wu yɛ̂ŋ laa wu gee chuule la. Nɛ wu gee chuule, fɛ wu chîaase ye fɛ kikwɛɛ ke le. Geenɛ keefɛ wu fêge kikwɛɛ ke bɛ muh mu gɛ.
\v 5 Bɛŋ kêe lɛ muh wuchii kɛme ki wu tûude we ntɛ.
\p 
\v 6 Nɛ muh yɛyi muh bɛ jɛ yi Nyo, muh wù ba yɛyi wu gâdɛ mwɛɛ mwe mù njoŋe munchii, wu nyâ muh wù yɛyi wu yu.
\p 
\v 7 Keefɛ bɛŋ lɛ̂ɛde bɛ bikwɛɛ biɛna gɛ. Gɛ Nyo nyu kiyuŋ gɛ. Bɛŋ kêe lɛ fiɛɛ fì muh bone le gɛh fi fì wu lé wu gê wu gwêjɛ.
\v 8 Nɛ muh bone ye ŋgo nyu fiɛɛ fì nyaŋ yi ye ye goone, tu wu lé wu gê wu gwêjɛ gɛh nyu fiɛɛ fì nyaŋ yi ye ye nyaa, fì le kwe. Nɛ muh bone ye ŋgo nyu fiɛɛ fì Kiyo ki Nyo goone, tu wu lé wu gê wu gwêjɛ kinche kì kage gɛ kì Kiyo ki Nyo nyaa.
\v 9 Noo, keefɛ besabɛŋ gê be wɛ̂ɛyi ki be gêe mwɛɛ mù njoŋe gɛ, nje kife le ki tô ki kôjɛ kì bee kɛ̂mɛ ŋgwejɛ wuyu fɛ bee baaŋ fwɛɛŋ gɛ.
\v 10 Fi mo fi nyu lɛ, yi kife le kichii kì besabɛŋ kɛme je, bee gêe gɛh mwɛɛ mù njoŋe fɛ bamii le bachii tete fɛ bobaa bò le a kfuu chi bamii ba mbɛmɛ le.
\s1 Njɛmɛ wù fɛkimɛsɛ
\p 
\v 11 Bɛŋ yɛŋ no ajii a ŋwa a fɛnɛ le a kuge! Saŋ mɛ bɛ kibo kaŋ.
\v 12 Bamii baa bò kaane lɛ ba chvûse bɛŋ yeh le bo bò goone ki bo chîaase ye yi mwɛɛ mu nyaŋ yi ye le. Bo gee noo wu lɛ keefɛ bamii gê bo bôone bikaa a bo jiŋ nje fiɛɛ fì bo feeji lɛ Kletu gɛ̀ kwe yi kintaaŋ le.
\v 13 Mo bamii ba ba le ba chvuu wa bo yeh, gɛ bo gɛɛde banchi bachii gɛ. Geenɛ bo goone lɛ sege ba chvuu bɛŋ yeh bo mo bo kfûune gvuu lɛ bɛŋ le bɛŋ ge fiɛɛ fì bo goone yi ye yene le.
\v 14 Geenɛ, fɛ mɛne gɛ mɛ nyu n'yu ntô ŋkfûuŋ gvuu yi fiɛɛ fimi le fuge yi saaka wu lɛ Tada wese besabɛŋ wù Jiso Kletu gɛ kwe yi kintaaŋ le. Le yi kintaaŋ kinɛ le wù mwɛɛ mu yi nshɛŋ le, le mu kwe wa mu gasɛ besa mu, ŋgasɛ tɛ bɛ mu.
\v 15 Nɛ muh le yu wù ba le ba chvuu wu yeh kɛnɛ ba baaŋ wu yeh chvuu gɛ, tu gɛ fifiɛɛ kɛme fiɛɛ ki fi gê gɛ. Fiɛɛ fì le fishaŋ le lɛ, Nyo sêesɛ muh, wu nyûme muh wù fwɛŋ.
\v 16 Kimbonɛ ki Nyo bɛ yii ye tô fɛ bamii bachii ba bii je yinɛ le, bò le wa bamii ba Ishwala ba Nyo.
\p 
\v 17 Kɛge mɛɛse gɛɛne lo, keefɛ muh ka wu fûuŋse mɛ gɛ, nje banlelɛ ba le yi ye yaŋ le duunyi lɛ nle muh wu Jiso.
\p 
\v 18 Booŋ ba bwɛɛŋ, Tada wese besabɛŋ wù Jiso Kletu dûnyɛ fitele fì joŋe fɛ biyo biɛna le. Fi nyûme noo.
